{"id": "1466989878968582274", "channel_id": "1464238310481465355", "type": 19, "author_id": "139343733714845697", "author_name": "satachan", "author_bot": false, "content": "The reason i feel that way is in relation to both the dev's track record and what I've seen in other games.\n\nI am concerned about AA becoming a second passive that it makes a character's kit unfinished.\n\nIt really does go back to the simple concept of, why gate a buff that can heavily impact how you'd play a character.\n\nBut now it is here to stay, I am taking light's word on how he'll take responsibility for if the balance breaks. \n\nIf a concern is real and needed clarification, then it isnt really fearmongering.  This was just the tip of the iceberg crashing into the ship. One single update doesnt change a playerbase's view. It is cumulative. \n\nI got the statement I asked for, I can now be cautiously optimistic about it.", "timestamp": "2026-01-31T02:54:02.500000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["590233814580592796"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1466505942375071978", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1464238310481465355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Regarding the possible +12 Paywall", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801", "1181168197425172480", "1361169005435420785"]}
